    <h2 class="section-title">Not-igniting repair costs.</h2>
    <p class="lead">$120 outdoor diagnostic, waived with repair. Universal pricing across residential and commercial. Duty cycle (residential 50-200 hr/yr vs commercial 8-14 hr daily) affects parts wear timeline, not diagnostic pricing.</p>
